headline: Truist Downgrades Jack In the Box Amid Slowing Same Store Sales
summary: Jack in the Box Inc.’s (NASDAQ:JACK) woes in the market have taken a turn for the worst. On May 27, Truist downgraded the stock from a Buy to a Hold, slashing the price target by more than half to $22 from $51. The downgrade is in response to the stock’s underperformance as the company struggles […]
